data.description: Cute one story brick home in Newport with a ton of potential! As you enter the front door you are greeted with a beautiful floor to ceiling brick fireplace, centered in the large living room/family room. The bedrooms are a split floorpan style, having the master on one side of the house and the additional bedrooms on the other. Very functional floor plan. The backyard is a great size, and fully fenced. Home needs some updating and TLC but is in overall good condition!
